{"word":"ἐκλιπής","slug":"ἐκλιπής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκλιπής</b></el> <el>(ἐκλῐπής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>ἐκλῐπεῖν</el> aor2 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> of <a href='S:ἐκλείπω'><el>ἐκλείπω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>failing, deficient</i>, <el>ἡλίου ἐκλιπές τι ἐγένετο</el><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ἔκλειψις'><el>ἔκλειψις</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>omitted, overlooked</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}